Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------text-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的名字是古屋螢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天開始上高中一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我有个以引為豪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一個作為班委團結著班級的很厲害的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然因為太過認真找不到女朋友很可憐就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:25.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,古屋君 又在同一個班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:28.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川同學 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:29.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:31.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我哥哥承蒙你關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這麼客氣 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 只是客套話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:45.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥 這個人誰 只是同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,關係好嗎 還有其他女性朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:49.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 螢 很沒禮貌耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你很喜歡你哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:53.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈? 你在說啥? 這很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:55.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 這傢伙是兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是挺好的嗎 挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以你是我哥的什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:02.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:08.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,莫非難道說 你們兩個在交往中?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 我們只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我早就覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:14.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,暫時唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是沒有得到回應 所以說是暫時啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:26.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這傢伙在耍著你玩 怎麼回應早就想好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 快點拒絕她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,讓她懷有希望很可憐的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢… 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是啊古屋君 要拒絕的話就快點吖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:46.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 我 並 並不是對皆川同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拒絕她 拒絕她 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也 也不是不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我在擔心你啊為什麼就不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你在被玩弄 就算交往也只會受傷而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:05.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢 並不是說要交往唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我這是被拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,女朋友什麼的不需要吧 因為有我就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 皆川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我沒辦法輕鬆說出交往吧這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為交往之後那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,結婚什麼的 沒有經濟能力的話孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我們的事情你已經考慮到這種地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然不是這樣的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是因為我哥人比較認真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是啊 真的很認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:33.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以才喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我再試著等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小螢 能先幫我看著麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可以 我不會把哥哥讓給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒關係的唷 我會一起疼愛你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是討厭!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我沒什麼特別喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能熱衷的興趣和愛好也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我自己都覺得自己是無聊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是大家真的有那麼多喜歡的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:11.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看起來喜歡星星呢 要不要加入天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 並沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 嘛 只是聊聊天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,決定了要加什麼社團了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:23.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那要不要來看看星之管弦樂呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 玩笑過頭啦!? 啊勒勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看星星很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那是當然啊 這麼好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是只是看的話不會厭倦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,會厭倦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有別的特點什麼的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有! 簡單地說就是天文部很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在脫單率高達100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 是不是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩你並不是那麼喜歡星星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那為什麼要在天文部?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:02.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 你看 我喜歡天文部的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 還有些什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜託了! 反正你沒有其他其他想加的社團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我說一個讓你對星星感興趣的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:18.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那塊區域有一個叫做角宿一的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看起來是一個非常大的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:29.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但其實是兩顆相互環繞吸引的星星喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,兩顆星星共同努力的話就可以發出如此耀眼的光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是不是有點哲學味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:35.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有興趣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn方正喵鸣\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明完全照抄學長的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有其他的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn方正喵鸣\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明感覺受教了很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看火星時吃的章魚燒 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:55.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已經畢業了的前輩說什麼火星人應該就像章魚一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以就一邊看火星一邊烤章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:02.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn方正喵鸣\bord1.2\c&H00050606}然後一邊看火星一邊烤章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是前輩一直在看火星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我一個人大口大口地吃完了
Comment: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是前輩一直在看火星 所以我一個人大口大口地吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}然後前輩就超級生氣 本來他平時臉就好可怕了啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}其他的比如還有秋天賞月呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:15.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏天一邊熱火超天地講著外星人的恐怖故事一遍吃冰棒什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已經跟星星沒有關係了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對這個人而言 天文部是真的非常喜歡的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也能像這樣熱衷於什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:23.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加賀也來嘛 肯定很會有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我沒有什麼特別喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一邊覺得這樣的自己很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一邊尋找著自己喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這就是我在尋找的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:44.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總而言之我 想要多看看這份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:49.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,鄰座的上根同學 總是迴避著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:09.82,title - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord3.5\3c&H00474849\fs70\b0\fad(0,1000)\pos(1000,595.619)\b1}隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根還不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,馬 馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不願和我對上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我做了什麼不好的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還是趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛 剛田君!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:24.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的隱形眼鏡掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:29.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我出去的時候會注意不踩到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:32.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想要你陪我一起找啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明白了 一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我沒被討厭嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你經常掉隱形眼鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:42.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如想要擦擦汗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這汗確實不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實你有話想對我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我已經做好準備 盡全力回應上根的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想說什麼就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,既然你都說道這種份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,應該已經知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在暫時 還沒什麼頭緒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前上課的時候呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我因為眼睛不好正在苦惱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你把筆記借給我過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那件事怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為 好溫柔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是多管閒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有注意到真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才沒有! 不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找隱形眼鏡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,至少請讓我幫你找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答覆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:51.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答覆?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 也沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的感情 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也只是想傳達給你而已… 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這意思是 想看到我的誠意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不至於
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是 想知道剛田的想法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:07.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果這樣能得到你的原諒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:19.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我其實 一直都理解不了女生的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 沒那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果再接近你的話 肯定會給你添更多麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這麼沒用的我 以後還是承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哼～ 隱形眼鏡找到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:41.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎麼哭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才你是 能和我交往的意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交往?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顧的話 肯定是要交往的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝謝——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 上根??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我說的話很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 我這邊才是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我還沒 好好的告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註釋：告白在日語本意是說出實話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:12.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 有什麼話想說就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,未報的雨 落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 沒帶傘嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,同班的菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,幾乎沒和他說過什麼話
Comment: 0,0:01:04.04,0:10:37.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H007D7D7D\bord5\blur3\fs90\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b0\fad(500,0)\pos(989.943,489.886)}雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:38.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,借給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 跑回去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:42.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為感覺很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,中途還是一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 和女生一起回家的話會很難堪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也沒有 和高野一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:02.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 和我這種人傳不出什麼緋聞的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:03.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,肩膀淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:08.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那再靠近點?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 再近點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 不會不好意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和男生 這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 也沒人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 要是被喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:27.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到了之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 我也沒這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎麼笑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,戀愛這種事情我不是太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你要是被表白了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種人不存在的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是假設啦 假設你被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概會拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:53.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為 對我這種人表白 他肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我又不可愛 又陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有這種事!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野你幫別人做衛生什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,每天照顧班裡的青鱂魚之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我 對高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我要在這裡坐公車了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才 你對我說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣 那拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:28.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,戀愛嗎… 對我來說太勉強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君這麼溫柔 肯定很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:33.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才 要對你說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是決定要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 我對高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你是在 鼓勵我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:58.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:03.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我在這裡下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:10.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君這個人 真是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,作為借傘的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,給他做點餅乾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 至近距離戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.08,title - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord3.5\3c&H00474849\fs60\b0\fad(500,0)\pos(641.334,456.952)}至近距離戀愛
